Cook pasta as package directs; drain. Meanwhile, in 13 x 9-inch baking pan, combine oil, garlic salt, oregano and crushed red pepper. Add potatoes and onion to pan; stir to coat. Roast at 425 degrees F for 15 minutes. Stir in Mann's Stringless Sugar Snap Peas; roast 5 minutes. Stir in broth; roast 5 minutes. Remove from oven. Add cooked pasta; stir to combine. Place in large serving bowl; sprinkle with cheese, as desired.